snippet.title: Legendary Eleven Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for Legendary Eleven, an ​epic arcade football game inspired by the golden age of football spanning the 70's to the 90's. Choose from 36 teams full of glorious haircuts, moustaches and legends in short shorts. Lead them to glory and win the World Cup!

Soon available in Steam Early Access (May the 15th, 2018) and Switch (June the 8th, 2018) with PS4 and Xbox One coming later this year!
